[src:abac-access-control/provisioning-technology] Cloud users can obtain cloud services through a cloud service catalog or a self-service portal.
[src:abac-access-control/provisioning-technology] Because business users can obtain and configure cloud services themselves, this means IT staff can be more productive and gives them more time to manage cloud infrastructures.
